Class XMLCharacters

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.batik.xml.XMLCharacters
Direct Known Subclasses:
XMLUtilities
public class XMLCharacters
extends Object

This class contains the definitions of the arrays used to find the type of the characters found in an XML document.
